syntax enable " syntax highlighting makes it easier to tell what is what in VIM
set tabstop=4 " number of spaces per tab
set softtabstop=4 " numbers of spaces created/deleted when pressing <TAB> or delete a tab
set expandtab " <TAB> is just a shortcut for 4 spaces
set number " add line numbers
set cursorline " highlight current line
set showmatch " highlight [{()}]
set incsearch " search as characters are entered
set hlsearch " highlight matches
colorscheme desert

